## Quick Start

```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd {{ project_name | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}
./batten install
```

## Development

```bash
./batten status             # Show stack configuration
./batten lint               # Run all linters
./batten test               # Run all tests
./batten format             # Auto-format code
./batten security-scan      # Run security scanners
./batten hooks run          # Run pre-commit hooks
./batten context refresh    # Update AI context files
{% if mempalace_enabled %}./batten memory status      # MemPalace status
./batten context live       # Sync MemPalace to context files
{% endif %}```

Filter by language:

```bash
./batten lint --lang python
./batten test --lang go
```

## Stack Configuration

Edit `batten.yml` to change your engineering stack, then regenerate:

```bash
./batten status             # What's configured now
./batten diff               # Preview changes
./batten regenerate         # Apply changes
```

