## Workflow

This project uses the Batten tiered workflow. See [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) for details.

| Tier | Scope | Review |
|------|-------|--------|
| **S** | Schema, security, infra | Human required |
| **A** | New features | Human required |
| **B** | Enhancements | Auto-merge if CI green |
| **C** | Docs, typos | Auto-merge if CI green |
{% if gstack_enabled %}
Use `/review` before PRs and `/ship` to land changes.
